TestOnErrorRetry
/ Verifies that error.handle modifier retries a failing action
- set %counter% = 0
- call IncrementAndFail
    on error retry 3 times
    on error ignore
/ After 3 retries + original = counter should be 4
- assert %counter% equals 4

IncrementAndFail
- set %counter% = %counter% + 1
- throw error 'intentional failure'
